      "content": "hey im having a weird issue with my shopify theme. on mobile the product image is totally overlapping the title text in the product section. i tried messing with the margins in the base.css but nothing is working. can u look at this snippet and tell me why it's happening?\n\n.product-single__media {\n  display: block;\n  width: 100%;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n}\n\n.product-single__title {\n  font-size: 24px;\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 1;\n}\n\n@media only screen and (max-width: 749px) {\n  .product-single__media {\n    float: left;\n    width: 50%;\n  }\n}",
